name: A Collection Of Cool Songs I Like
name_original: A Collection Of Cool Songs I Like
description:
I dont really know what to call this. Its like a music player in a visual novel? I guess. It has a couple of songs i like. 

no gameplay really.  you just kinda click and the next song plays.

songs

Bye. by J Dilla

Dead Man's Tetris by Flying Lotus

TRUST! by JPEGMAFIA

Meanwhile by Gorillaz

Some by Steve Lacy

Crabs In A Bucket by Vince Staples

Easter Sunday by Zelooperz
